OL,3,CGuernsey government authority hits
OL,4,Cback at criticism over stockpile
OL,5,Crejection
OL,7,FGuernsey's Development and Planning
OL,8,FAuthority (DPA) has hit back at
OL,9,Fcriticism after it rejected plans to
OL,10,Ftemporarily stockpile inert waste at
OL,11,FLongue Hougue.
OL,13,FIt comes after the board that oversees
OL,14,FGuernsey's waste disposal, the States'
OL,15,FTrading Supervisory Board (STSB), said
OL,16,Fit would appeal the decision on 25
OL,17,FJuly.
