OL,3,CGuernsey government authority hits
OL,4,Cback at criticism over stockpile
OL,5,Crejection
OL,7,FThe STSB's president, Dep Peter
OL,8,FRoffey, said he would enter
OL,9,F'constructive' negotiations over the
OL,10,FDPA's decision to try and find a
OL,11,Fresolution which avoided taking the
OL,12,Fdecision back to the States.
OL,14,FThe board fears a lack of space for
OL,15,Fthe disposal of inert waste, including
OL,16,Fbuilding materials, will put pressure
OL,17,Fon the island's construction industry.
