OL,7,FThe STSB put forward the application
OL,8,Fin March 2024 for a stockpiling site
OL,9,Fat Longue Hougue which could be used
OL,10,Ffor up to three years with another
OL,11,Fthree years being allocated to clear
OL,12,Fit.
OL,14,FThe States failed to secure a
OL,15,Fpermanent site for inert waste during
OL,16,Fthe last term.
