OL,3,CGuernsey government authority hits
OL,4,Cback at criticism over stockpile
OL,5,Crejection
OL,7,FA statement from the DPA today (29
OL,8,FJuly), which is part of Guernsey's
OL,9,Fgovernment, said: "We share Dep
OL,10,FRoffey's disappointment that the
OL,11,FStates has yet to find a solution for
OL,12,Fthe disposal of inert waste.
OL,14,F"However, the fact that there was no
OL,15,Fopposition expressed to Guernsey
OL,16,FWaste's temporary stockpiling
OL,17,Fapplication does not remove the need
OL,18,Ffor us to consider the application on
OL,19,Fpolicy grounds.
