OL,7,F"The reasons for the refusal of this
OL,8,Fapplication were outlined at the
OL,9,Fmeeting and are now published online.
OL,11,F"We are still hopeful that a workable
OL,12,Fsolution can be found and remain very
OL,13,Fwilling to work constructively and
OL,14,Fcollaboratively with the STSB to that
OL,15,Fend."
