OL,4,Cback at criticism over stockpile
OL,5,Crejection
OL,7,FIn a notification of refusal of
OL,8,Fplanning permission letter on 22 July,
OL,9,Fthe DPA says it is concerned that
OL,10,Fproposals for the temporary stockpile
OL,11,Fare neither 'minor' nor
OL,12,F'inconsequential' and did not comply
OL,13,Fwith the Island Development Plan.
