OL,3,CGuernsey government authority hits
OL,4,Cback at criticism over stockpile
OL,5,Crejection
OL,7,FFollowing the On 25 July, Dep Roffey
OL,8,Fsaid the STSB would call for a "less
OL,9,Fconfrontational way forward if at all
OL,10,Fpossible, but that cannot include a
OL,11,Frevised, scaled down, application
OL,12,Fwhich fails to address the island's
OL,13,Fstrategic needs in respect of inert
OL,14,Fwaste. That would simply be
OL,15,Firresponsible."
OL,17,FDep Roffey added that the application
OL,18,Fcould not be scaled back would put the
OL,19,FSTSB's ability to provide adequate
OL,20,Fwaste facilities on the island at risk.
