OL,7,FIf no resolution is found between the
OL,8,FDPA and the STSB the issue will be
OL,9,Ftaken to the States, which could
OL,10,Fdirect the DPA to reverse or amend its
OL,11,Fdecision.
OL,13,FThat debate cannot take place until
OL,14,FSeptember at the earliest when the
OL,15,Fnext States meeting will take place.
